    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait i think i got mixed up. i meant how do i find the relative major of a minor key using the circle? like if i know the key is c minor, how do i use those intervals/steps in the circle to figure out the major key that goes with it? i'm having trouble visualizing the movement around the circle.",
